# **09  Accessibility requirements (unchanged from v1.0)**

| **Requirement** | **Standard** | **Implementation** |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Touch target minimum** | 48×48px | All icons wrapped in 48×48px touchable zones |
| **Colour contrast — body text** | 4.5:1 minimum | #1C1C1E on #FAFAF5: 16.2:1. #6B6B6B on #FAFAF5: 5.8:1. |
| **Screen reader** | All images need alt text | Food photo: alt = dish name. Icons: accessibilityLabel on all icon buttons. |
| **Reduced motion** | System setting respected | All animations reduced to instant state changes or 100ms opacity fades. |
| **Font scaling** | Up to 200% | Use relative units (sp). Test layout at 200% font scale. |
| **Error identification** | Never colour-only | Always pair error colour with icon and text. |
| **Language** | en-IN locale | Date format: DD Month YYYY. Currency: ₹. |

